    <mxCell id="sf" value="&lt;b&gt;Salesforce CRM&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:9px;color:#555&quot;&gt;[External System | Salesforce Lightning]&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:9px;color:#444&quot;&gt;Agent UI. Authenticates via SAML.&lt;br&gt;Sends internal JWT with &lt;b&gt;chase.role&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;to ForgeRock on token exchange.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Calls Case Manager with:&lt;br&gt;• OBO token (customer / partyKey)&lt;br&gt;• Colleague token (non-customer)&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0f0f0;strokeColor=#888888;fontColor=#333333;fontSize=11;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=4;spacingTop=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
